bal Prod-ucts Network, complemented by the WHO recom-mendations.\nAlternative medicine\ninteresante libro sobre herbolarios y plantas medicinales escrito de una forma clara y accesible\nLoading Preview\nSorry, preview is currently unavailable. You can download the paper by clicking the button above.\nMEDICINA ALTERNATIVA, INTEGRATIVA OU COMPLEMENTAR TEXTOS REUNIDOS - 2\u00aa edi\u00e7\u00e3o\n2019 \u2022\nActa Farmac\u00e9utica \u2026\n2003 \u2022\nFeminismo/s\n2007 \u2022\nAnales de la Facultad de Medicina\n2013 \u2022\nLas Terapias Complementarias en la esfera p\u00fablica.\n2019 \u2022\n2009 \u2022\nRevista M\u00e9dica de la Universidad de Costa Rica\n2008 \u2022\nPerspectivas de la Comunicaci\u00f3n\nPhysis: Revista de Sa\u00fade Coletiva\nHistoria de los medicamentos\n2016 \u2022", "language": null, "image": "http://a.academia-assets.com/images/open-graph-icons/fb-paper.gif", "pagetype": "article", "links": ["https://www.academia.edu/privacy", "https://www.academia.edu/upgrade-browser", "javascript:void(0)", "https://www.academia.edu/signup", "https://www.academia.edu/", "https://www.academia.edu/login", "https://www.academia.edu/signup", "https://www.academia.edu/login", "https://www.academia.edu/signup", "https://www.academia.edu/Jobs", "https://www.academia.edu/about", "https://www.academia.edu/press", "https://medium.com/@academia", "https://www.academia.edu/Directory/People", "https://www.academia.edu/Directory/Papers", "https://www.academia.edu/terms", "https://www.academia.edu/privacy", "https://www.academia.edu/copyright", "https://www.academia.edu/hiring", "https://support.academia.edu/", "https://www.academia.edu/attachments/71956466/download_file?st=MTY5NTQzODcxOCwyMTcuMjM4LjEzMS4yNDY%3D&s=swp-splash-paper-cover", "https://independent.academia.edu/AMANDAASUNCIONLOVERAARELLANO", "https://www.academia.edu/34557604/2_0_1_4_2_0_2_3_Estrategia_de_la_OMS_sobre_medicina_tradicional", "https://independent.academia.edu/JuanJos%C3%A9GilFern%C3%A1ndez", "https: